OL,3,CYork and Hull amongst worst areas for
OL,4,Cpharmacy closures
OL,6,FYork, Hull, and Wakefield are amongst
OL,7,Fthe worst areas in the country for
OL,8,Fpharmacy closures, new data has
OL,9,Frevealed.
OL,11,FThe National Pharmacy Association
OL,12,F(NPA) looked at the number of closures
OL,13,Fin the last three years, with
OL,14,FLiverpool coming out on top:
OL,16,FThis has left England's pharmacy
OL,17,Fnetwork at its smallest for 20 years.
