OL,3,CYork and Hull amongst worst areas for
OL,4,Cpharmacy closures
OL,6,FHe said the increasing waiting lists
OL,7,Fcould lead to some people not getting
OL,8,Fthe help they need.
OL,10,F"Some medication can be for mental
OL,11,Fhealth - if it's an ordeal to get your
OL,12,Fmedication, you might just not take it
OL,13,Fand see what happens."
OL,15,FPharmacies and council leaders are
OL,16,Fwarning that patients in areas with
OL,17,Fthe highest health needs have been
OL,18,Fworst impacted by a 'tidal wave' of
OL,19,Fpharmacy closures in the last three
OL,20,Fyears, with the risk of this widening
OL,21,Fhealth inequalities.
