OL,3,CYork and Hull amongst worst areas for
OL,4,Cpharmacy closures
OL,6,FMr Picard said: "Deprived areas and
OL,7,Frural areas tend to see a greater
OL,8,Fdemand on community pharmacies.
OL,10,F"Health deprivation we know means that
OL,11,Fpeople live with longer term
OL,12,Fconditions, they really have to be
OL,13,Flooked after, and are more demanding
OL,14,Fon NHS resources.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, because of the way
OL,17,Fpharmacies are remunerated, being
OL,18,Fbusier doesn't necessarily mean that
OL,19,Fyou make more money."
