OL,3,CYork and Hull amongst worst areas for
OL,4,Cpharmacy closures
OL,6,FThe NPA is calling on the government
OL,7,Fto provide an urgent funding uplift.
OL,9,FMr Picard said: "The government needs
OL,10,Fto fund community pharmacies properly
OL,11,Fso they stop closing.
OL,13,F"We need the government to step in and
OL,14,Fstabilise the network. You can't add
OL,15,Ficing on the crumbly cake, you need to
OL,16,Fstabilise the cake in the first place,
OL,17,Fand I think this is really what we're
OL,18,Fcalling for today in order to save our
OL,19,Fcommunities from pharmacies closing."
