OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Community
OL,8,Fpharmacists are at the heart of local
OL,9,Fhealthcare and through our 10 Year
OL,10,FHealth Plan, we will ensure they play
OL,11,Fan even greater role as we bring more
OL,12,Fcare out of hospitals and closer to
OL,13,Fwhere people live.
OL,15,F"This year we've increased funding to
OL,16,Fcommunity pharmacies by 19% to almost
OL,17,F#3.1 billion ` the largest uplift in
OL,18,Ffunding for any part of the NHS - so
OL,19,Four dedicated pharmacists can provide
OL,20,Feasy access to high-quality care to
OL,21,Fall."
